  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/376afb8b0ec73c99cf7251f8350dffdf.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/376afb8b0ec73c99cf7251f8350dffdf.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/376afb8b0ec73c99cf7251f8350dffdf.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Segment World, Unique Tag Action</strong><br>In The Segment World, Each stage has two backgrounds that coexist in a segmented form. Each background separates into the twin zones. You can do tag action through segments and use each style of attack.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/ce26d01311db4874f4230ce97b9aa4a3.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/ce26d01311db4874f4230ce97b9aa4a3.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/ce26d01311db4874f4230ce97b9aa4a3.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Mush Hunter Twins, \"Matilda\" and \"Amanda\"</strong><br>These are twin girls who make a living by eradicating Mush. The twin girls have a \"Sword Master\" and \"Gunslinger\" attack style.<br><br><br><strong>Stylish and Hit Satisfaction</strong><br>The game is fast-paced in classic arcade format. You can feel a good hit satisfaction as the battle is the main one.<br><br><br><strong>Toon Style Graphics</strong><br>It features unique graphics that mimic Comics' feelings, including halftone and glitch effects.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/76753f6c3934804fabca8b0e82e5fc1c.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/76753f6c3934804fabca8b0e82e5fc1c.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/76753f6c3934804fabca8b0e82e5fc1c.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Various Mush and Five Charming Bosses</strong><br>Defeat various types of mush and defeat overwhelming bosses!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/9f4bc97890b102dde3c7bf82c304e266.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/9f4bc97890b102dde3c7bf82c304e266.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/9f4bc97890b102dde3c7bf82c304e266.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/376afb8b0ec73c99cf7251f8350dffdf.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/376afb8b0ec73c99cf7251f8350dffdf.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/376afb8b0ec73c99cf7251f8350dffdf.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Segment World, Unique Tag Action</strong><br>In The Segment World, Each stage has two backgrounds that coexist in a segmented form. Each background separates into the twin zones. You can do tag action through segments and use each style of attack.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/ce26d01311db4874f4230ce97b9aa4a3.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/ce26d01311db4874f4230ce97b9aa4a3.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/ce26d01311db4874f4230ce97b9aa4a3.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Mush Hunter Twins, \"Matilda\" and \"Amanda\"</strong><br>These are twin girls who make a living by eradicating Mush. The twin girls have a \"Sword Master\" and \"Gunslinger\" attack style.<br><br><br><strong>Stylish and Hit Satisfaction</strong><br>The game is fast-paced in classic arcade format. You can feel a good hit satisfaction as the battle is the main one.<br><br><br><strong>Toon Style Graphics</strong><br>It features unique graphics that mimic Comics' feelings, including halftone and glitch effects.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/76753f6c3934804fabca8b0e82e5fc1c.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/76753f6c3934804fabca8b0e82e5fc1c.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/76753f6c3934804fabca8b0e82e5fc1c.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Various Mush and Five Charming Bosses</strong><br>Defeat various types of mush and defeat overwhelming bosses!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/9f4bc97890b102dde3c7bf82c304e266.poster.avif?t=1705038085\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/9f4bc97890b102dde3c7bf82c304e266.webm?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305490/extras/9f4bc97890b102dde3c7bf82c304e266.mp4?t=1705038085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
